title: Oscar Peterson on the loss of Ray Charles: CBC Archives | CBC
description:
In this clip from 2004, legendary Canadian jazz pianist Oscar Peterson reflects on the death of a fellow jazz giant, American Ray Charles. For more classic clips, go to http://www.cbc.ca/archives
